## API Reference

| Method | Endpoint            | Auth? | Description              |
|--------|---------------------|-------|--------------------------|
| POST   | /api/register       | No    | Create account           |
| POST   | /api/login          | No    | Login                    |
| POST   | /api/logout         | No    | Logout                   |
| GET    | /api/me             | Yes   | Get current user info    |
| GET    | /api/menu           | No    | Get menu items           |
| POST   | /api/reservations   | Yes   | Book a table             |
| GET    | /api/reservations   | Yes   | View your reservations   |
| DELETE | /api/reservations/:id | Yes | Cancel a reservation   |
| POST   | /api/orders         | Yes   | Place an order           |
| GET    | /api/orders         | Yes   | View your orders         |
| POST   | /api/reviews        | Yes   | Submit a review          |
| GET    | /api/reviews        | No    | View all reviews         |

